@167 /*The tall brick walls lined with thick metal beams close upon you from both sides, encasing you in a narrow corridor. Walking through the reddish smoke, you come upon a makeshift construction made of barbed wire at the corridor's mouth on the other end. It does not close the gap completely, but it narrows it down quite significantly. Ulfbrand signals everyone to stop. */
=@168 /*A moment of tense calm follows, like the innocent, playful silence before a storm that destroys everything. */
==g-bbd156 @169 /*"FATED! MY BERSËRKERS!" Ulfbrand roars at the top of his deep voice. "WE ARE AT OUR ENEMIES' GATES. GET READY!" [g-15602] */
