==g-bbd189 IF~Global("G-AmbushdakkonLoc6","GLOBAL",3)~THEN @483 /*You and Dak'kon make a great team. So far, no one has been able to even get close to the actors. You are holding the rear in a stable position, at least until Ulfbrand himself breaks through here. */
