==g-bbd189 @486 /*The spectacle in the center of the battlefield, which has captured everyone's attention, is nearing a thrilling conclusion. The leader of the Fated, Ulfbrand Völgarsson Baunaætari, wrestles the chain beast to the ground. The Sinkers, deprived of the support of their mages who now have their own problems, are unable to stop him from completing his work of destruction. The Ysgardian tears the metal creature to pieces and hurls them into the ranks of the Doomguard. He is now free to act. */
==g-bbd189 @487 /*And he does... */
==g-bbd189 @488 /*Emboldened by the berserkers' chant, he runs forward and picks up a lost axe from the ground. As the Ysgardians make room for their leader, he smashes into the defense with a wide cut. The first Doomlord tries to parry, but the axe tears right through his entropy blade and his neck, also cutting into two of the soldiers behind him. Ulfbrand is now fueled by the ecstasy of battle rage. */
==g-bbd189 @489 /*Is there anyone who can stop this? */
