==g-bbd189 IF~Global("g-batgod","GLOBAL",2)~THEN @491 /*A well-armed squadron of the Godsmen on the right flank remains at the ready. */
==g-bbd189 IF~Global("g-bathar","GLOBAL",2)~THEN @492 /*Near the fortifications, a unit of Harmonium officers lurks in a tight formation. They have moved closer to the conflict, waiting to see how the situation develops.  */
